        <div class="bg-indigo-600 p-6 text-white flex justify-between items-start rounded-t-2xl">
            <div>
                <h3 class="text-xl font-bold">¬øC√≥mo te sientes?</h3>
                <p class="text-indigo-200 text-xs mt-1">Registro diario de emociones</p>
            </div>
            <button onclick="toggleModal('checkinModal')" class="text-white/70 hover:text-white bg-white/10 hover:bg-white/20 rounded-lg p-1 w-8 h-8 flex items-center justify-center transition-colors">
